nodes.text: David Espinoza is a video game developer that is credited as a member of the Art team for Star Wars: Knights of the Old Republic II: The Sith Lords. He also served as a Senior Artist in the generalist department at Lucasfilm for Rogue One: A Star Wars Story, Solo: A Star Wars Story, Star Wars: The Rise of Skywalker, and season 2 of The Mandalorian.
